            "title": "緬甸地震︱實皆跨河橋「骨牌式」垮塌 　清真寺坍塌造成增至20人喪生︱有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/1e0a101d7b6625d0a550a651ce768e82/2025-03/262_23_.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/b04b78180bad71f0bfdf97c6360c0102/88009e6516f84deda432237813d85ad3-26376f315acb868ca81226b8b44f1ff7-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67e66a75f282c\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67e66a75f282e\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"緬甸地震︱實皆跨河橋「骨牌式」垮塌  寺廟倒冧已致至少20人身亡︱有片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3175e61b727ad0bdf861e82fdf2eb46f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032816533422151.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">緬甸地震︱實皆跨河橋「骨牌式」垮塌  寺廟倒冧已致至少20人身亡︱有片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>緬甸實皆省（Sagaing）西北部今日下午2時20分在發生7.9級地震，震源深度30公里。香港天文台則測定是次地震為7.3級。12分鐘後，再發生6.4級地震。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3441961/\">緬甸7.9級地震 泰國曼谷有大樓倒塌 雲南、河內有震感︱持續更新</a></strong>\n</p><h2>救援人員瓦礫救人</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"實皆有跨河大橋倒塌。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/098ba14abedc92f4d7e066c0a15ce09b/2025-03/262_23__1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        實皆有跨河大橋倒塌。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"救援人員努力從瓦礫救人。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ac08ce1f45984f84225fa426ed134f0/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_15_50_30_2__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        救援人員努力從瓦礫救人。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"瓦礫壓著汽車。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a39a45d5923e6985fe09fd6adb5e9780/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_15_50_30_1__0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        瓦礫壓著汽車。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"救援人員努力從瓦礫救人。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2b7ea4bd98b5d59c7d4dcd504210ab33/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_15_50_30_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Ima