a-library-item__name\">\n        地震後，緬甸有大量建築物倒冧。WhatsHappeningInMyanmar@X\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/271dbeefca2eee2f09fb3206876ec9fc/2025-03/214.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3598cd29445daac920cec0d49ec5d34e/2025-03/541.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/74f5536d98a3f2aae028bb0d8889e78f/2025-03/874_17_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>強烈地震地震猛烈，不僅鄰近泰國曼谷，緬甸市區亦造成嚴重破壞。網上流出影片所見，實皆省有跨河大橋（Sagaing Bridge，The Ava Bridge）倒塌，多區有多個建築物倒冧，包括不少寺廟。有救援人員從瓦礫救出滿面流血傷者，當局未有公布確實傷亡數字。\n\n</p>\n<p>據BNO NEWS報道，曼德勒一座清真寺遭震毀坍塌，造成至少20人死亡。另有曼德勒當地民眾通過社交媒體發布消息說，有一棟建築倒塌，四五人被困。 首都內比都部分學校和辦公樓倒塌。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3441980/\">緬甸地震｜泰國曼谷興建中大樓倒塌 泰媒稱至少43人被埋1人喪生｜有片</a></strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060785/即時-國際-緬甸地震︱實皆跨河橋-骨牌式-垮塌-清真寺坍塌造成增至20人喪生︱有片",
