        {
            "title": "緬甸地震｜泰國曼谷BTS地鐵停駛 車廂搖晃如「海盜船」｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/940a83cfb6cff8f5e154894dcc8d0f3f/2025-03/New_Project_22__1.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/30177f380bb371f0801387c6371c0102/dbcd0bdef27e44f9ae30f9171853170e-566790b4c0833dca8b03f04e4ce428b9-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67e6693327e54\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67e6693327e56\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"泰國曼谷BTS地鐵停駛，車廂搖晃如「海盜船」。 X@ChromeCrumpet\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f359febd1fe73d683cdace3b26140939/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032817091842030.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">泰國曼谷BTS地鐵停駛，車廂搖晃如「海盜船」。 X@ChromeCrumpet</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>緬甸今（28日）發生7.9級地震，鄰近國家震感強烈，泰國首都曼谷傳出施工中大樓瞬間倒榻、緬甸曼德勒（Mandalay）有大橋倒塌。除此之外，曼谷也被民眾拍下BTS地鐵強烈搖晃的驚駭畫面。\n\n</p><h2>BTS地鐵停駛</h2>\n<p>從網傳影片可見，一處車站停靠列車的車廂，紅色車廂劇烈搖晃，驟眼看還以為是機動遊戲設施。月台上有民眾緊張得手牽著手維持穩定，生怕站不穩，也有民眾貼出BTS地鐵站鐵門拉下鐵閘的畫面，指出目前BTS地鐵停駛中。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3441980/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E6%9B%BC%E8%B0%B7%E8%88%88%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E5%80%92%E5%A1%8C-%E6%B3%B0%E5%AA%92%E7%A8%B1%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9143%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E5%9F%8B1%E4%BA%BA%E5%96%AA%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C